WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:04.680
Conversation D. Can I help you?

00:04.680 --> 00:09.680
Yes. I'd like to buy tickets to London, please.

00:09.680 --> 00:11.680
When would you like to fly?

00:11.680 --> 00:13.760
On the 5th of May.

00:13.760 --> 00:17.160
The 5th? Let me see.

00:17.160 --> 00:24.640
Hmm, I'm sorry. We don't have any flights to London on that day. What about the

00:24.640 --> 00:30.240
4th? No, I can't leave before the 5th.

00:30.240 --> 00:33.400
Then we have a flight on the 6th.

00:33.400 --> 00:35.040
What's the flight number?

00:35.040 --> 00:39.200
It's CA 757.

00:39.200 --> 00:43.240
CA 757.

00:43.240 --> 00:46.640
At what time does it leave Shanghai?

00:46.640 --> 00:52.800
It takes off at 12.55. How many seats please?

00:52.800 --> 00:55.200
I'd like three seats.

00:55.200 --> 00:56.400
Just a moment please.

